<emphasis id="193CA6EC51431C5B7277E63D1B0718CC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">Oreocharis wenshanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
W.H.Chen &amp; Y.M.Shui, sp. nov. 
<emphasis id="E2A09D87AA4CFF1CF7C9C4CC2A3E63EC" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">A</emphasis>
plant 
<emphasis id="DCDC18D15B764526355D89ADD0537ABD" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">B</emphasis>
opened corolla showing stamens and staminode 
<emphasis id="F50A3E3161A112614A43324BFAEB4C9E" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">C</emphasis>
pistil showing ovary, disc and stigma 
<emphasis id="FBF8F2BF38E208AF190C25F9DCD2B92B" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">D</emphasis>
